Date: 1999-06-22

Title: Derivative expansion of quadratic operators in a general 't Hooft gauge

Authors: Vasilios Zarikas

Comments: 40 pages, to appear in Phys. Rev. D

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D60 (1999) 106001

A derivative expansion technique is developed to compute functionaldeterminants of quadratic operators, non diagonal in spacetime indices. Thiskind of operators arise in general 't Hooft gauge fixed Lagrangians. Elaborateapplications of the developed derivative expansion are presented.